	   <tr><td colspan=2>2h practice sword is nice at your lvl next weapon you want to look for 2hs wise is one with lower delay maybe a drakkel forged bastard sword. they are dropped and velious and sell for about 125 plat. not a bad price for a 20/45 weapon. you said you have no 1hs weapon this needs to be your big move. if you have not practiced this skill in a couple of levels you have a lot of catching up to do. 1hs/bash cambo is the main paladin but you always keep 2hs up to date because of of the quest swords like soulfire, FA, and FD. get in a group and use a 1hs you want speed the lower the dly the better if you need get 5 or so lvls of skills up get a fine steel short sword or the like and get in a group that isnt killing magical creatures. you need to get in to a guild as soon as possible you are almost ready for ghoulbane and you will NOT beable to camp that alone untile you are lvl 45ish, and by that time you want the sword of mourning. anyways get your skill up fine a guild /who all "guildname" see if there are any high lvl paladins in that guild or do "/who all paladin" and see what paladins are online get in there guild. we tend to help each other out. i have a lvl 25 paladin in my guild now as soon as she reaches 27 or 28 we are going to get ghoulbane. your guild will help you do this too. <br><br>sorry i got long winded and off subject some here, i hope it helped. <br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Celtpirate Waverider<br>34 paladin<br>saryrn-Boche Morte<br>Yoshiro<br>15 cleric<br>saryrn-House of Wargoth</td></tr>
