	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello Fellow Pally's ) First I must disagree about the 1hs/bash combo. Im a 40th lvl dwarf and only use 2hs. I have always had an ok weapon growing up but all 2hs I never put any practice points into 1hs or had a 1hs weapon but I must say that Im a bad lil dude. I now wield the Blade of Xalgoz 23/40 and I hit regurlarly for 98 points dmg ) I can solo or group either way (good armor and resists are the key) Not the weapon! Its a big help but not the main thing for a Paladin. As you all grow a bit more you will understand this. Try dueling a necro of same lvl with an ok amount of resists as opposed to having great resists. The diff is Jaw dropping. So my point to this is 2hs will kill that nec before ur resists run out and he finally does get fear off in which case You are dead, alot quicker than than 1hs which if you use he will cast on you before you kill him. Also 2hs weapons are the main weapon for Pally's FD and FA and such are the best Pally weapons. I would max out 2hs before even starting 1hs. As far as Guild is concerned, You would do better aquireing weapons in a guild instead of not in a guild and the company is great if ur in the right one so choose your guild wisely ) Hope I helped )<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
